cd database

# Build
"node_modules/.bin/webpack" 

# Hot Build
npx webpack --watch -o "./public_html/"

# Serve HotReload Static/Local Server:
serve public_html/



Integration into game should be relatively simple:
put bundle.js into game, and use the functions written there to CRUD.

You can get an ID from profile:me, which is likely unique 
    https://itch.io/docs/api/serverside#reference/profileme-httpsitchioapi1keyme